
GUILDS
======

This is a table of contents for the rules about guilds in Genesis.  
There are four files, each covering three subtopics. The command 
"man -k guild*" will list all manual entries about guilds. 

guilds1  - types of guilds, 
         - entering and leaving guilds, 
         - atmosphere and wizard involvement

guilds2  - tax: the one basic rule governing all major guilds
         - implementation
         - the layman branch of an occupational guild

guilds3  - skills
         - guild stats
         - guild council

guilds4  - adventurers guilds
         - documentation
         - remarks

